  "title": "Therapist",
  "description": "<p>We're offering a dynamic Therapist role designed for those eager to grow their career and expand their skillset. This is more than just a job — it's a chance to learn unique, in-demand techniques that will set you apart in the industry. You'll receive exclusive training from an international expert, specially flown in to provide hands-on coaching and mentorship. Whether you're just starting out or looking to take your expertise to the next level, this role is your gateway to long-term success in the beauty industry.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Highlights:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Overall Salary Package (With Basic + Incentive + Sales Comms)</li>\n  <li>Provide systematic training (Both Theory &amp; Hands-on) related to TCM concept</li>\n  <li>Fun &amp; dynamic culture</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote range of beauty and wellness products and service</li>\n  <li>Perform professional skin and body analysis for client</li>\n  <li>Deliver facial, body, aesthetic treatments tailored to client needs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Relevant certifications (CIDESCO, CIBTEC, ITEC, etc.) will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and retail hours</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
